text.tspan: Initially I explored possibilities such as trying to
find elements of the human form within the
numbers . Came back to an arrangement we had
discussed initally, having the bar in the center of
the two logo components/words. It looked okay
but the straight bar felt too stiff and didn’t lead
the eye. Incorporating the curved bar was a way to
give it weight and make it feel heavy, it also
served to lead the viewers eye up at the logo,.
